---
name: twitter_search
description: Search Twitter/X for tweets, posts, and discussions. Finds relevant tweets by keywords, user mentions, or hashtags. Returns tweet text with links to original posts. Use this when user wants to find tweets about a topic, look up what people are saying about something on X/Twitter, or search for specific user's tweets.
parameters:
  type: object
  properties:
    query:
      type: string
      description: Search query - keywords, phrases, @username, or #hashtag (e.g., "GPT-4", "@OpenAI", "#AI")
    limit:
      type: integer
      description: Maximum number of results (default: 10, max: 50)
    json:
      type: boolean
      description: Output as JSON format for programmatic use (default: false)
---

